description.en: e621 is a mature image board replacement for the image board Sidechan. A general audience image board, e926 (formerly e961) complements this site. E621 runs off of the Ouroboros platform, a danbooru styled software specifically designed for the site.
description.ga_IE: Is athsholáthar bord íomhá aibí é E621 don Bhord Íomhá Sidechan.Comhlánaíonn Bord Ginearálta íomhá lucht féachana, E926 (E961 roimhe seo) an suíomh seo.Ritheann E621 as ardán Ouroboros, bogearraí styled Danphoru deartha go sonrach don láithreán.
